Class Puzzle

  • java.lang.Object
    • Puzzle

  • public class Puzzle
extends java.lang.Object
    Puzzle is a class which represents a Puzzle It contains its current configuration as well as its destination configuration It also contains its optimal route from start to destination - IFF it has been solved Created by Toby Leheup on 28/02/14.
    Version:
    28/02/2014
    Author:
    Toby Leheup - TL258
